## 2ct Lab-Grown vs Natural: The $13,680 Decision

The lab arbitrage at 2ct is the most dramatic in the market. A natural 2ct G-VS2 costs $16,490. An IGI 2ct D-VVS1 lab costs $2,810 (ID [28629934](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/28629934?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)). That's $13,680 in savings — for a stone that is physically, chemically, and optically identical to the natural under every test. The only difference is origin.

