| D-FL | IGI | $5,190 | [29372746](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29372746?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | 8.1mm | Flawless on certificate, still 69% cheaper than natural G-VS2 |
